---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Korea Tax Guide for Foreigners, a static information website that does not require accounts or collect sensitive tax information.">
  <main class="section narrow article">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>This website does not require user accounts and does not ask visitors to submit sensitive tax information.</p>
    <p>At this stage, the site is a static information website. It does not currently provide login accounts, payment features, comments, consultation forms, or document uploads.</p>
    <p>If analytics, advertising, embedded third-party tools, or contact forms are added later, this policy should be updated to explain what data is collected, why it is collected, and how visitors can manage their choices.</p>
    <p>Do not send personal tax records, identification documents, visa documents, or private financial information through unsecured channels.</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
